{"tid":1026442,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"防彈直播到一半背後門打開 私生飯「也在直播」探頭狂拍","createTime":"2019-02-18T06:26:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-18T15:25:52.000Z","uid":74065,"like":2,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"6f782266f2b4b9f4f4a15970e106136680aa4d42","tid":1026442,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T06:26:36.000Z","msg":"南韓團體BTS防彈少年團雖然總是感謝粉絲力挺，但遇到這種狀況應該是笑不出來！最近他們在直播慶祝團員J-Hope生日，與粉絲互動時，鏡頭一個畫面閃過後方的門口，竟然有一鬼影探頭，嚇翻網友，等到重播慢速觀看，照到的畫面更讓人毛骨悚然！<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3903/d3903030.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3903%2Fd3903030.jpg&h=21ab7470&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n▲防彈直播到一半，背後照到黑影。（圖／翻攝自vlive）<br />\n<br />\nBTS正在日本福岡舉辦巡迴演唱會，適逢成員J-HOPE生日，演唱會結束後，他特別在飯店房間內開直播和粉絲一起倒數，迎接25歲（實歲）的到來，直播半小時後，成員們突然拿出蛋糕，唱著生日快樂歌走進來，讓他超級驚喜。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/sxnrays/status/1097171633582817280?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw%7Ctwcamp%5Etweetembed%7Ctwterm%5E1097171633582817280&amp;ref_url=https%3A%2F%2Fstar.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F1380640\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsxnrays%2Fstatus%2F1097171633582817280%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%257Ctwcamp%255Etweetembed%257Ctwterm%255E1097171633582817280%26ref_url%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fstar.ettoday.net%252Fnews%252F1380640&d=8lKb2kYWDOzPE5G8cc2TgBZhTFX1FVJLw6RhI%2FCRHR8%3D&h=03d2cbe5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsxnrays%2Fstatus%2F1097171633582817280%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%257Ctwcamp%255Etweetembed%257Ctwterm%255E1097171633582817280%26ref_url%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fstar.ettoday.net%252Fnews%252F1380640&h=bcee044b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/sxnrays/status/1097171633582817280?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw%7Ctwcamp%5Etweetembed%7Ctwterm%5E1097171633582817280&amp;ref_url=https%3A%2F%2Fstar.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F1380640</a><br />\n<br />\n不過直播到一半，畫面照到飯店門口，本來就沒有全關的大門，突然有一個黑影探頭進來，就有粉絲慢速播放後發現，是一個長髮女子，而且她還拿著手機往裡面拍！粉絲立馬聯想到這個女人可能就是傳說中會侵犯藝人隱私的「私生飯」，曾聽說有私生飯偷偷潛入成員柾國房間，在飯店床上跳來跳去，讓這支影片在粉絲間引起譁然。<br />\n<br />\n不過也有粉絲持相反立場，認為對方只是工作人員，網友截圖直播的後半段，當各個成員陸續走出J-Hope房間，Jimin再度回來叫柾國離開時，就有拍到Jimin和一位拿著錄影機的女子站在門口，粉絲猜測「如果是私生飯，肯定不會讓她這樣拍吧？」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3903/d3903035.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3903%2Fd3903035.jpg&h=694b7a14&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲有粉絲直指那位探頭的的確是私生飯。（圖／翻攝自推特）<br />\n<br />\n然而也有其他粉絲找出證據表示，「不能確定和Jimin一起的女子是否就是前面探頭的那位女子，因為已經有人找到那位探頭女子朋友的IG，在限時動態上PO出該女的背影寫著：她vlive開始後潛進房間，裡面瞬間爆笑。」似乎證實有人混進房間周遭，還說她正在拿手機直播闖入偶像房間的實況，消息傳出後讓粉絲全都氣炸！<br />\n<br />\n屌你偷影床照都得啦咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1ad73806435b43d5242fd84e1396b8c7a53331d","tid":1026442,"uid":19209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T06:37:06.000Z","msg":"點解會開到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03510af6b318936f17931bd678c651ecf4ad85c9","tid":1026442,"uid":193951,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T06:42:31.000Z","msg":"我趁v仔訓覺嗰陣入佢間房射精佢"},{"pid":"49ea93913f8c3e8eec6615d6f19ce847dfcb2075","tid":1026442,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"03510af6b318936f17931bd678c651ecf4ad85c9","tid":1026442,"uid":193951,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T06:42:31.000Z","msg":"我趁v仔訓覺嗰陣入佢間房射精佢"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T07:57:25.000Z","msg":"諗起都勃起左"},{"pid":"dc98bab8e3468aa4e06811311a6564dc76d53898","tid":1026442,"uid":107913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T07:58:54.000Z","msg":"肯定係雞黎 玩8p"},{"pid":"d855e97e98097baf261e2068ba7e246fbc430be0","tid":1026442,"uid":52073,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"49ea93913f8c3e8eec6615d6f19ce847dfcb2075","tid":1026442,"uid":74065,"lik